    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely bittersweet about letting go of my pride and joy. This beauty has been my weekend baby, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single Sunday. Honestly, it still has that fresh, new-car feel that\u2019s getting harder and harder to find. There's a tiny, barely-there stone chip on the hood from one of our highway cruises, but you'd have to really squint to see it! It\u2019s been impeccably maintained and runs like an absolute dream. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have\u2014come by, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
