      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit boasts a surgical maintenance history with the critical rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements already performed using VAC Motorsports components. The high-revving 4.0L powerplant delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a lightning-fast M-DCT transmission that has been flashed with the GTS software for optimized shift points. The chassis rigidity is uncompromising, sitting on an EDC-equipped suspension that offers a perfect balance between track-ready damping and grand touring compliance. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and meticulous ceramic coating. This is a turn-key specimen for the discerning collector looking for peak mechanical harmony.",
      "price": 47850.0,
